Dialogue: 4,0:16:48.34,0:16:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo budem robiť, keď sa stretnem s Anaru?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:54.02,0:16:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, vitaj—
Dialogue: 4,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:02.46,0:17:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My by sme sa mali ospravedlniť, že sme k vám prišli tak náhle.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moji rodičia sú hlúpi.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja mama sotva opúšťa dom.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.50,0:17:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že sa nechce s nikým stretnúť.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:16.76,0:17:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja viem, že je to ťažké, pretože Nee-chan zomrela, ale je to už trochu nechutné.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanbím sa za moju mamu.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:27.56,0:17:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj je záhada, že ako rodičia premýšľajú.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale myslím si, že to majú ťažké.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rodičia, myslím... možno, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:39.68,0:17:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemám právo niečo také hovoriť...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majú ešte jedno dieťa.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Syna.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:51.21,0:17:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som ešte dieťa a sotva sa pamätám na Nee-chan,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:56.88,0:18:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ale pamätám sa na niečo.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odchádzam!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja tiež!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja idem tiež!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty nie, Saa-kun!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja idem!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:14.73,0:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... tvoja sestra je súčasťou Super ochráncov mieru!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeme chrániť každé jedno miesto!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:22.89,0:18:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže Saa-kun, musíš chrániť náš dom. Rozumieš?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedala mi, aby som ochraňoval náš dom, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to také smutné...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anjou—
Dialogue: 4,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, prišiel si.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:04.71,0:19:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ste všetci...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si dnes robil celý deň?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Pracoval som...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:10.24,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si si istý, že si nevolal zo svojho domu?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Volal?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostali sme aspoň 5 tichých hovorov.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiché?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:21.24,0:19:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak čo, budeš nám hovoriť, že to urobila Menma?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale otec a ja sme boli obaja už vtedy...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže to bola Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to s tebou?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma {\i1}toto{\i0}, Menma {\i1}tamto{\i0}...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:38.23,0:19:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...huh?!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:40.99,0:19:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, ukáž mi ju.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma je tu, nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže mi ju ukáž!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň, Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upokoj sa!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upokoj sa trochu.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už zase? Naozaj?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, prestaň už!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si hrozný, Yadomi.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty sa stále ešte hráš na to, že je Menma tu?!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie—
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa, všetkým.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo sa ospravedlňuješ?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma je tu, Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo, ty tiež už prestaň!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, beriem si čas.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.23,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu, trochu sa upokoj!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men—
Dialogue: 4,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi ťa prosím...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veľmi ťa prosím...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:48.73,0:20:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň... už.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:52.84,0:20:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To, čo sa stalo nezmizne po zvyšok našich životov.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma sa neospravedlňuje, ty klamár.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:00.83,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je šanca, aby nám Menma odpustila!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:05.84,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Denník?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:10.61,0:21:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo? Veď nefúka vietor.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaňte už.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale naozaj, prečo...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.97,0:21:24.32,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\pos(26,56)\fs38\an7\be6}Naše leto sa skončilo.
