Dialogue: 4,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej, Jin-tan.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:01.49,0:22:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu naozaj... Menma?
